question: I feel like I have something stuck in my ear, everytime I blow air out my ear try to it makes strange noises?
question_content: I feel like I have something stuck in my ear, everytime I blow air out my ear try to it makes strange noises?

answers.answer_content: That happens to me when I have nasal congestion. Is your nose stuffy maybe that's why.   Or is could possibly been tight or tense neck muscles. It also maybe an inner ear infection ( I had that once but there was no pain). If I keeps happening you should bring it up with you doctor. Hope that helps.
